## Description {#details}

A wrapper class for inspecting calls to intrinsic functions.

This allows the standard isa/dyncast/cast functionality to work with calls to intrinsic functions.

Definition at line 48 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/intrinsicinst-h">IntrinsicInst.h</a>.
